phi]</code> Component Library for Delphi that encapsulate the classes for access to WMI of Windows in a set of VCL. BiosInfo, PrinterInfo, DiskInfo, etc. Allow access WMI Classes: WIN32_Bios, WIN32_Printers, WIN32_DiskDrive.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-19T13:16:24.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"Fr0sT-Brutal/awesome-pascal","categoryHTML":"<h2>Debugging / error handling</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MahdiSafsafi/DebugEngine\">DebugEngine</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/MahdiSafsafi/DebugEngine\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">155</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":155,\"repo\":\"MahdiSafsafi/DebugEngine\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->. <code>[Delphi]</code> Collection of utilities related to debug stuff (stack trace, CPU registers snapshot, debug info, etc). Accessing Delphi debug info, Getting address of symbol from its name, Delphi map parsing and map converter to binary format, Smart stack trace, Delphi exception stack trace hook, etc.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-19T13:16:24.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rust-embedded/awesome-embedded-rust","categoryHTML":"<h2>Peripheral Access Crates</h2><h3>NXP</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/SKEAZN642\"><code>SKEAZN642</code></a> Peripheral access API for KEA64 family microcontrollers (generated using svd2rust) - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/crates/v/SKEAZN642.svg\" alt=\"crates.io\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-19T11:16:03.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"markusschanta/aweso